text: Yesterday my friend and I chose to take a cruise on our scooters around the Kennesaw Mountain area, just a few miles from our homes, and we stopped for lunch. There on the wall was a picture of two old men sitting at a table in the very same eatery. It looked like a movie still, so I looked more closely at the men. They did look familiar, but then the waitress told us that picture was from a movie filmed here in Georgia, and the men were Robert Redford and Nick Nolte...
